        "input": "对比 Redux Toolkit、Zustand、Jotai 三种方案，并给出使用示例",
        "output": "## 状态管理方案对比\n\n### 方案对比表\n\n| 特性 | Redux Toolkit | Zustand | Jotai |\n|------|--------------|---------|-------|\n| 包大小 | ~15KB | ~1KB | ~3KB |\n| 样板代码 | 中等 | 极少 | 少 |\n| 学习曲线 | 陡峭 | 平缓 | 中等 |\n| 性能 | 中等 | 好 | 优秀 |\n| DevTools | 优秀 | 支持 | 支持 |\n| TypeScript | 优秀 | 优秀 | 优秀 |\n| 适用场景 | 大型应用 | 中小型应用 | 细粒度更新 |\n\n### 1. Redux Toolkit 示例\n```typescript\n// store/counterSlice.ts\nimport { createSlice, createAsyncThunk } from '@reduxjs/toolkit';\n\ninterface CounterState {\n  value: number;\n  loading: boolean;\n}\n\nconst initialState: CounterState = {\n  value: 0,\n  loading: false\n};\n\nexport const fetchCount = createAsyncThunk(\n  'counter/fetchCount',\n  async () => {\n    const res = await fetch('/api/count');\n    return res.json();\n  }\n);\n\nconst counterSlice = createSlice({\n  name: 'counter',\n  initialState,\n  reducers: {\n    increment: (state) => {\n      state.value += 1;\n    },\n    decrement: (state) => {\n      state.value -= 1;\n    }\n  },\n  extraReducers: (builder) => {\n    builder\n      .addCase(fetchCount.pending, (state) => {\n        state.loading = true;\n      })\n      .addCase(fetchCount.fulfilled, (state, action) => {\n        state.value = action.payload;\n        state.loading = false;\n      });\n  }\n});\n\nexport const { increment, decrement } = counterSlice.actions;\nexport default counterSlice.reducer;\n\n// 使用\nconst count = useSelector((state) => state.counter.value);\ndispatch(increment());\n```\n\n### 2. Zustand 示例\n```typescript\n// stores/useCounterStore.ts\nimport { create } from 'zustand';\n\ninterface CounterState {\n  count: number;\n  loading: boolean;\n  increment: () => void;\n  decrement: () => void;\n  fetchCount: () => Promise<void>;\n}\n\nexport const useCounterStore = create<CounterState>((set, get) => ({\n  count: 0,\n  loading: false,\n  \n  increment: () => set((state) => ({ count: state.count + 1 })),\n  \n  decrement: () => set((state) => ({ count: state.count - 1 })),\n  \n  fetchCount: async () => {\n    set({ loading: true });\n    const res = await fetch('/api/count');\n    const data = await res.json();\n    set({ count: data, loading: false });\n  }\n}));\n\n// 使用 - 组件中\nconst { count, increment, fetchCount } = useCounterStore();\n\n// 选择器优化性能\nconst count = useCounterStore((state) => state.count);\n```\n\n### 3. Jotai 示例\n```typescript\n// atoms/counter.ts\nimport { atom } from 'jotai';\n\nexport const countAtom = atom(0);\nexport const loadingAtom = atom(false);\n\n// 异步 atom\nexport const fetchCountAtom = atom(\n  async (get) => {\n    const res = await fetch('/api/count');\n    return res.json();\n  }\n);\n\n// 派生 atom\nexport const doubledCountAtom = atom((get) => get(countAtom) * 2);\n\n// 使用\nimport { useAtom } from 'jotai';\n\nfunction Counter() {\n  const [count, setCount] = useAtom(countAtom);\n  const [doubled] = useAtom(doubledCountAtom);\n  \n  return (\n    <div>\n      <p>Count: {count}</p>\n      <p>Doubled: {doubled}</p>\n      <button onClick={() => setCount(c => c + 1)}>+</button>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n```\n\n### 选型建议\n\n**选择 Redux Toolkit 当：**\n- 大型复杂应用\n- 需要时间旅行调试\n- 团队熟悉 Redux 模式\n- 需要强大的中间件生态\n\n**选择 Zustand 当：**\n- 追求简洁 API\n- 中小型应用\n- 需要快速开发\n- 不想写样板代码\n\n**选择 Jotai 当：**\n- 需要细粒度更新\n- 原子化状态管理\n- 性能敏感场景\n- 喜欢函数式风格"
