      {
        "input": "设计一个响应式的产品卡片组件，在移动端单列，平板双列，桌面三列",
        "output": "## 响应式产品卡片组件\n\n### 1. CSS Grid 方案（推荐）\n```css\n/* 产品网格容器 */\n.product-grid {\n  display: grid;\n  gap: 1.5rem;\n  /* 移动优先：默认单列 */\n  grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n  padding: 1rem;\n}\n\n/* 平板：双列 */\n@media (min-width: 768px) {\n  .product-grid {\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n  }\n}\n\n/* 桌面：三列 */\n@media (min-width: 1024px) {\n  .product-grid {\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n  }\n}\n\n/* 大屏：四列 */\n@media (min-width: 1440px) {\n  .product-grid {\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 2. 现代方案 - auto-fit + minmax\n```css\n.product-grid {\n  display: grid;\n  gap: 1.5rem;\n  /* 自动适应：每列最小 280px，最大 1fr */\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n  padding: 1rem;\n}\n```\n\n### 3. 完整组件实现\n```html\n<div class=\"product-grid\">\n  <article class=\"product-card\">\n    <div class=\"product-image\">\n      <img \n        src=\"product.jpg\" \n        alt=\"产品名称\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n      <span class=\"badge\">新品</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"product-info\">\n      <h3 class=\"product-title\">产品名称</h3>\n      <p class=\"product-description\">简短描述...</p>\n      <div class=\"product-price\">\n        <span class=\"current\">¥299</span>\n        <span class=\"original\">¥399</span>\n      </div>\n      <button class=\"add-to-cart\">加入购物车</button>\n    </div>\n  </article>\n</div>\n```\n\n```css\n.product-card {\n  background: white;\n  border-radius: 12px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n  transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;\n}\n\n.product-card:hover {\n  transform: translateY(-4px);\n  box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n}\n\n.product-image {\n  position: relative;\n  aspect-ratio: 1;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.product-image img {\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 100%;\n  object-fit: cover;\n  transition: transform 0.3s;\n}\n\n.product-card:hover .product-image img {\n  transform: scale(1.05);\n}\n\n.badge {\n  position: absolute;\n  top: 10px;\n  left: 10px;\n  background: #ff4757;\n  color: white;\n  padding: 4px 8px;\n  border-radius: 4px;\n  font-size: 0.75rem;\n}\n\n.product-info {\n  padding: 1rem;\n}\n\n.product-title {\n  font-size: 1rem;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n  /* 文本截断 */\n  display: -webkit-box;\n  -webkit-line-clamp: 2;\n  -webkit-box-orient: vertical;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.product-description {\n  font-size: 0.875rem;\n  color: #666;\n  margin-bottom: 1rem;\n  /* 响应式字体 */\n  font-size: clamp(0.75rem, 2vw, 0.875rem);\n}\n\n.product-price {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 0.5rem;\n  margin-bottom: 1rem;\n}\n\n.current {\n  font-size: 1.25rem;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: #ff4757;\n}\n\n.original {\n  font-size: 0.875rem;\n  color: #999;\n  text-decoration: line-through;\n}\n\n.add-to-cart {\n  width: 100%;\n  padding: 0.75rem;\n  background: #2ed573;\n  color: white;\n  border: none;\n  border-radius: 8px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  transition: background 0.2s;\n}\n\n.add-to-cart:hover {\n  background: #26af61;\n}\n```\n\n### 4. 容器查询方案（现代浏览器）\n```css\n.product-grid {\n  display: grid;\n  gap: 1.5rem;\n  container-type: inline-size;\n}\n\n.product-card {\n  /* 根据容器宽度调整布局 */\n}\n\n@container (min-width: 400px) {\n  .product-card {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: row;\n  }\n  \n  .product-image {\n    width: 200px;\n    aspect-ratio: auto;\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 5. 响应式图片\n```html\n<picture>\n  <source \n    media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" \n    srcset=\"product-large.jpg\"\n  />\n  <source \n    media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" \n    srcset=\"product-medium.jpg\"\n  />\n  <img \n    src=\"product-small.jpg\" \n    alt=\"产品\"\n    loading=\"lazy\"\n  />\n</picture>\n\n<!-- 或使用 srcset -->\n<img \n  src=\"product-500.jpg\"\n  srcset=\"product-500.jpg 500w,\n          product-800.jpg 800w,\n          product-1200.jpg 1200w\"\n  sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw,\n         (max-width: 1024px) 50vw,\n         33vw\"\n  alt=\"产品\"\n/>\n```"
      }
